# Test 


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
?log
result <- log(1.4, base = 8.3)
result <- round(result, 3)
result %% 0.05
```

```
[1] 0.009
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
value <- 5
value / result
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] 31.44654
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
(ceiling(value) / result) / (floor(value) / result)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] 1
```
